      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NvSPZl-PbLc"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/NvSPZl-PbLc/maxresdefault.jpg" /></a></p><br /><p style="clear: both"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NvSPZl-PbLc"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/NvSPZl-PbLc/0.jpg" /></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NvSPZl-PbLc"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/NvSPZl-PbLc/1.jpg" /></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NvSPZl-PbLc"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/NvSPZl-PbLc/2.jpg" /></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NvSPZl-PbLc"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/NvSPZl-PbLc/3.jpg" /></a></p><br />
<hr style="clear:both" />

<p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><strong># 影片開始</strong></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">大家好～我們是蛙家。買回家的收納盒。你能好好的使用嗎。還是會覺得哪裡怪怪的。使用起來不太順手呢。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">今天要跟大家介紹。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">N個神助攻收納品搭配技巧。或許你家的收納盒。加上這些小物就會更好用喔。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">看下去之前。還沒訂閱的朋友記得先訂閱。並開啟小鈴鐺喔。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">第一款神搭配組合。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_25.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=25" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合1：大箱加小箱</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">是無印良品超人氣的。「軟質聚乙烯收納盒」。加上大創「半透明收納盒」。較深的無印收納盒。不容易分類。可以在下層收納備品。再放上2組大創分格盒。超簡單組裝完成！小改造就能收納蜜粉。眼影盤、口紅等小物。也可以收剪刀、膠帶。釘書機、筆等文具。超實用組合搭配。價格只要百圓即可。這招快學起來！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">第二款神搭配組合。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_54.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=54" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合2：居家醫藥箱</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">用大創的「卡片收納盒」。加上原先用作襪子收納的。「組合式收納盒」。一一放入無印良品的「PP化妝盒」。就變成超整齊的居家常備藥箱。大創的「卡片收納盒」有厚薄兩種。薄的可以收納常備藥丸。厚的收納指甲剪、OK繃跟感冒藥。「組合式收納盒」則可以收納。經常拿取的酒精跟噴劑等。大箱的容量放得下襪子盒2個。以及卡盒數個。後面還有空間放保健食品。加上標籤貼紙。所有物品一目了然。超整齊！如果想把這種。一包包的調味料袋收納在箱子裡。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_93.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=93" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合3：黏貼式分隔架</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">可以在深型的收納盒裡。加裝大創這款黏貼式分隔架在內側。第三款神搭配組合就完成囉！原先不好拿取的袋裝物品。全部變成直立式擺放。也不用擔心倒下溢出。小小加工一下就讓收納盒變更好用了！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">除了側邊。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">也可以加裝在底部喔~。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">超高人氣的無印檔案盒是居家收納好物。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_118.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=118" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合4：檔案盒加掀蓋盒</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">我們在蝦皮找到這款「掀蓋收納盒」。方形的尺寸跟方型的無印檔案盒是神搭配。放入3個掀蓋盒。第四款神搭配組合就完成囉！透明設計內容物一目了然。很適合收納經常需要拿取的小物。例如化妝棉、棉花棒、髮圈等。像是小零食、茶包也很適合這樣收納喔！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">大創的這款「冰箱瓶罐收納架」。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_145.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=145" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合5：冰箱瓶罐收納架</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">側邊附有把手的設計。不管是收納飲料還是調味料罐都超剛好！而且可以直立式收納在冰箱門。完美利用垂直空間。也很適合收納軟趴趴的耐熱袋跟保鮮袋。不同尺寸的袋子各自放一格。抽取使用也很方便。再搭配無印檔案盒裝在一起。放在廚房角落也不顯雜亂。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">如果是寬的無印檔案盒。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_173.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=173" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合6：文件分類</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">收納文件跟雜誌時容易混亂。可以搭配大創這款「檔案盒收納隔板」。只要夾上去。就能將文件好好分類。這款神搭配。組裝超簡單！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">收納隔板也可以加裝在冰箱側門。還有這種可伸縮的款式。可以適應不同的空間大小。輕鬆夾上。就能讓雜亂的食材乖乖站好！剛剛的這款檔案盒搭配附蓋收納盒。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_198.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=198" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合7：檔案盒收納隔板</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">也可以用隔板來改造一下。隔板寬度跟窄型檔案盒差不多。一樣加裝2個隔板上去。就能將小物件分類收納了！放在桌邊收納辦公物品。放在玄關也能收納。回家隨手亂丟的東西。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">無印寬版的檔案盒。也可以拿來收納衣架、洗衣袋等用品。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_220.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=220" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合8：大創書擋</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">但把東西全部放入。容易變得凌亂。搭配「大創書擋」使用。就可以將大、中、小。不同尺寸的洗衣袋分開收納。大創這款書擋外型很簡約。跟無印檔案盒風格相配。如果直接把書擋放入。使用時有可能會滑動。可以加裝大創這款「防震墊」。將這個防震墊黏貼在書擋底部。再將2個書擋放入檔案盒。從上面看是這樣。加裝墊片之後。使用時書擋就不會移動了。收納小妙招分享給大家！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">第九個神搭配組合要來解決。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_256.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=256" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合9：抽屜不掉落的秘訣</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">抽屜掉落的問題。無印良品這款pp資料盒很好用。但如果拖拉時太用力。抽屜會整個掉下來。可以搭配常見的文具「長尾夾」。夾在抽屜尾端的內側。拖拉抽屜時就可以穩穩的固定住。櫃體位移的問題。則可以用大創的這款「緩衝止滑墊」。在底部四個角各黏上一顆。就能夠有效止滑。使用時更安心。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">接下來的神搭配組合。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">使用的東西都可以。在大創、無印或文具店裡輕鬆買到。像是這款回收紙箱收納架。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_293.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=293" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合10：diy回收紙箱收納架</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">就是用2個大創的「T型書擋」來組裝。這款書擋高度有到19公分。搭配一樣在大創買的「黏貼式滑輪」。先黏在底部4個角落。再將這種大顆的強力磁鐵。吸附在其中一個書擋的內側。就可以把兩個書擋固定在一起了。因為是磁力固定。所以可以伸縮調整寬度。底下滾輪也很方便移動。收納紙箱超方便。平時還可以藏在居家縫隙角落。要回收時再拉出來就好。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_328.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=328" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合11：書擋收納妙招</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">書擋加上強力磁鐵還可以有更多利用。像是收納小鑷子、指甲剪。文具類用品也可以收納。搭配磁吸收納盒。就可以收湯勺、鍋鏟等。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">書擋倒過來放在層板上。搭配磁吸盒跟掛勾。棉花棒跟髮圈等小物。就能順手收在一起囉！將書擋卡在沙發或床的縫隙裡。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_348.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=348" target="_blank"><strong># 神搭配收納組合12：沙發縫隙收納</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">就是一個隱形的收納架。看到一半的書或雜誌。就可以順手收在這裡。遙控器背面黏上強力磁鐵。也可以一併收納在這個小面板上。這麼多種書擋收納小妙招。你學起來了嗎！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_364.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=364" target="_blank"><strong># 無印好物妙用1：無印牙刷架</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">最後。蛙編來分享幾個。無印跟大創商品意想不到的妙用。首先。是經常被嫌棄雞肋的。無印良品「牙刷架」。愛用的網友表示。牙刷站立收納不怕髒。還有不同顏色方便區分。另一部分的人則覺得。這款牙刷架容易傾倒。還有藏污納垢的問題。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">如果你也是買了牙刷架卻不喜歡的人。推薦你可以把牙刷架換到廚房使用。當作料理筷架其實蠻順手的喔！無印良品鉛筆盒。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_394.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=394" target="_blank"><strong># 無印好物妙用2：小物工具盒</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">是很多人學生時期的回憶。除了收納鉛筆等文具之外。容易壓爛的餅乾也可以用筆盒攜帶喔！想吃的小零食全部放入筆盒。有堅硬外殼保護。就不怕外出壓傷囉！大創的科技海綿是清潔的好幫手。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_410.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=410" target="_blank"><strong># 大創好物妙用1：科技海綿</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">沒想到。海綿居然也可以幫助收納。打開抽屜。雖然雜物都有使用小收納盒分類。但因為尺寸不合。所以中間有空隙。只要一打開抽屜。物品就會隨之移動。好啊雜！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">這時只要準備大創的科技海綿。切下需要的大小。像這樣的長條型。就可以塞到抽屜邊緣。將空隙補齊。打開抽屜時東西就不會再亂掉囉！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">化妝刷具除了統一收在筆筒裡。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/NvSPZl-PbLc_440.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/NvSPZl-PbLc&t=440" target="_blank"><strong># 大創好物妙用2：diy懸掛化妝刷具架</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">還可以怎麼收納呢？蛙編很喜歡像這樣懸掛式的刷具架。今天就來試試用大創伸縮桿DIY吧。先將伸縮桿固定在櫃子內側。再把刷具尾端稍微加工一下。將小顆的強力磁鐵用無痕膠帶固定住。完成！一一將刷具懸掛上去。不僅使用時順手。清洗完晾乾也方便！這個聰明小妙招分享給大家！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">以上分享16個神搭配組合及收納妙用。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">看完影片。你最喜歡哪一個妙招呢？歡迎在留言區跟我們討論。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">如果你喜歡今天的分享。歡迎點擊下方「超級感謝」。用行動支持我們。做更多實用的影片。也能追蹤IG獲得更多靈感喔。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">最後。記得鎖定蛙家每週三更新。我們下週見，掰掰～。</p>

